title: CASCA RTF
description:
This is my second attempt to create RTF ebooks. These are: 
01 - Eterternal Mercenary
02 - God Of Death
03 - War Lord
05 - Barbarian
06 - Persian
13 - Assassin
22 - Mongol

I have books 01 & 22. I created books 02, 03, 05, 06, & 13 from PDF files from torrents. I read through each one, edited as I read, I may have not changed all the errors, but I think I got most of them.With the RTF format, if you find any errors, you can fix them.

I hope you enjoy them.
